{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"790c479e74","title":"中国共产党云南省委员会关于成立省委整风领导小组的通知","origin":"根据文件翻印件打印。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"73182ebfbe","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":14,"articleId":"790c479e74"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"93cca4665d","name":"谢富治","type":"人物"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"96113104ad","type":"title","text":"中国共产党云南省委员会关于成立省委整风领导小组的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"790c479e74"},{"id":"3d09888e55","type":"subtitle","text":"机密程度 机密","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"790c479e74"},{"id":"023d4723e0","type":"paragraph","text":"主送 各地、市委、各直属企业党委、省委各部委、国家机关各党组、人民团体各党组、各直属机关党委、高校党委、各大学党委、党校、云南日报、新华分社、广播电台、党刊室。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"790c479e74"},{"id":"586aca4409","type":"subtitle","text":"关于成立省委整风领导小组的通知","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"790c479e74"},{"id":"61b80d421c","type":"paragraph","text":"一、为了加强对整风运动的领导，省委决定由谢富治、于一川、郑敦、孙雨亭、陈康、陈方、郑刚、薛韬、苟兴才、袁勃、马文东、黎韦12同志，组成省委整风领导小组，以谢富治同志为书记，于一川同志为副书记。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"790c479e74"},{"id":"4feeb6101a","type":"paragraph","text":"二、省级各机关一律按系统分由以下九个大组统一领导整风，各大组的划分和组长名单如下：","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"790c479e74"},{"id":"6b7d481fbd","type":"paragraph","text":"1、工业、交通、基建大组，组长黎韦；","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"790c479e74"},{"id":"b1ded88990","type":"paragraph","text":"2、农、林、水利、气象大组，组长郑刚；","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"790c479e74"},{"id":"b1f102a75e","type":"paragraph","text":"3、财政、金融、贸易大组，组长薛韬；","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"790c479e74"},{"id":"52114fb9d3","type":"paragraph","text":"4、民族工作大组，组长孙雨亭；","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"790c479e74"},{"id":"798dc85389","type":"paragraph","text":"5、文化、教育、卫生大组，组长马文东；","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"790c479e74"},{"id":"9c35897ae7","type":"paragraph","text":"6、民族党派、民主人士、对资改造和宗教工作大组，组长陈方；","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"790c479e74"},{"id":"f8f29c217f","type":"paragraph","text":"7、政法大组，组长苟兴才；","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"790c479e74"},{"id":"ef67734ace","type":"paragraph","text":"8、党委和群众团体机关大组，组长郑敦；","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"790c479e74"},{"id":"3720d44695","type":"paragraph","text":"9、军队系统大组，组长陈康。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"790c479e74"},{"id":"ac1ebb88dd","type":"paragraph","text":"各大组领导小组的名单，由各大组组长召集有关单位负责同志研究确定报省委批准。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"790c479e74"},{"id":"6f1a525afb","type":"paragraph","text":"三、组织省委整风领导小组办公室，为省委整风领导小组的日常办事机构，以袁勃同志为办公室主任，陈光逵同志为副主任。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"790c479e74"},{"id":"cb58534e39","type":"paragraph","text":" 省   委1957年5月14日","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"790c479e74"}],"page":{"id":"2e6a79b75f","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"790c479e74","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}